articles.title: Gift to Kim Jong Un from Russian Delegation
articles.content:
Gift to Kim Jong Un from Russian Delegation
						
 Pyongyang, October 23 (KCNA) -- The dear respected Kim Jong Un received a gift from the visiting delegation of ITAR-TASS of Russia.
					 It was handed over to an official concerned Tuesday by Deputy Director General Kleyn Alexander who is heading the delegation.
